content.rendered: New trees have been planted in the Corekees team. Thomas Prins and Steve Miranda started their internship at Corekees this month. Thomas will use his data analytic skills, whilst Steve will give our social media a boost. One thing is for sure, both gentlemen will do their best and help Corekees grow.
